{
  "stem": "13851.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans-- and the Americans came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they screamed, the Americans came!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are liberated!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was April the 11, 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were like brothers to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They helped set-- they set up a medical on the field.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They carry out my-- my-- my brother to a-- to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They tried to save his leg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was green already from the injury.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was-- they put an x-ray on me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They say I was very happy that the injury would have been through right by my heart.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it split from my heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was meant I should stay alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember one contact was-- it was American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried-- like your own brother would find you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tried to help with everything-- with medicine, with food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a lot of people, they didn't know themselves how-- they was eating a lot of meat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- they died. 'Cause they couldn't survive, because their stomach didn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I felt a little better, I went-- organize some jams, I remember, jams-- to very light food, because if I'm gonna eat-- I saw there were dying people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's what I-- little by little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, I was about 80 pounds-- in that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed in that hospital till we got well, on our feet, and-- And what did the Americans say to you?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did they know that had been a labor camp?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they-- they told us they didn't know it was a labor camp, because, I told you, the barracks were built of bricks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they bombarded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought it's a-- the-- the German soldiers, German SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
